commands.name: baseprojectile.fullstartingmagazine
commands.description: Disables/Enables a full magazine when you start with a weapon. The default starting ammunition is <50% full mag.

commands.name: cargoships.startegressing
commands.description: Forces the current Cargo Ship to exit the map, following the 'egress_duration' rules.

commands.name: chat.enabled
commands.description: Disables/Enables the chat in game.

commands.name: craft.adddefaultblueprint
commands.description: Adds the item to the player’s inventory upon spawning.

commands.name: craft.banitem
commands.description: Bans the item from spawning. More info here.

commands.name: craft.CanUseRecycler
commands.description: Disable/Enable all of the recyclers functionality.

commands.name: craft.listbanneditems
commands.description: Lists the current set of banned items for the server.

commands.name: craft.listdefaultblueprint
commands.description: Lists the current set of default blueprints for the server.

commands.name: craft.removedefaultblueprint
commands.description: Removes the item from the list of default items on spawn.

commands.name: craft.unbanitem
commands.description: Removes the item from the banned item list.

commands.name: dropcrate.heli_setdropzone
commands.description: Sets the next Chinook Code Locked Crate drop zone to be at the specified monument.

commands.name: entity.deleteby
commands.description: Obliterates all buildings created by the target ID. Enter a Gamertag or PSN ID.

commands.name: entity.find_entity
commands.description: Prints a list of all items/animals/objects, etc. and their IDs & locations to the console log.

commands.name: entity.find_group
commands.description: Prints a list of all objects in a specified group and their IDs & locations to the console log.

commands.name: entity.find_id
commands.description: Finds an object based on its ID. You can find the ID from using find_entity.

commands.name: entity.find_parent
commands.description: Finds an object’s parent, based on its ID.

commands.name: entity.find_self
commands.description: Finds information about the player who entered this command.

commands.name: events.stopevent
commands.description: Stops the specified event.

commands.name: events.triggerevent
commands.description: Starts the specified event.

commands.name: global.dayview
commands.description: Disables/Enables eternal daylight for the player who entered it, regardless of server time.

commands.name: global.ent
commands.description: Runs the following commands: kill, lock, unlock, who, changecode, changeguestcode.

commands.name: global.moderatorid
commands.description: Grants the target Gamertag/PSN ID Moderator (Tier 2) Auth Level.

commands.name: global.mutevoice
commands.description: Disables Voice Chat features for a target Gamertag/PSN ID

commands.name: global.removemoderator
commands.description: Revokes Moderator (Tier 2) Auth Level from the target Gamertag/PSN ID.

commands.name: global.removevip
commands.description: Revokes VIP (Tier 1) Auth Level from the target Gamertag/PSN ID.

commands.name: global.say
commands.description: Displays the given message in the server chat box, that will be seen by all players.

commands.name: global.skipqueue
commands.description: Allows the target Gamertag/PSN ID to skip the queue when the server is full.

commands.name: global.teleport
commands.description: Teleports the chosen Gamertag/PSN ID to a chosen location.

commands.name: global.unmutechat
commands.description: Re-enables Quick Chat features for a target Gamertag/PSN ID.

commands.name: global.unmutevoice
commands.description: Re-enables Voice Chat features for a target Gamertag/PSN ID.

commands.name: global.vipid
commands.description: Grants the target Gamertag/PSN ID VIP (Tier 1) Auth Level.

commands.name: heli.call
commands.description: Summons the Attack Helicopter to roam the map.

commands.name: heli.calltome
commands.description: Calls the Attack Helicopter to patrol the area around the player who entered the command.
